n" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/elisabetta-pietrobon/" title="View all posts by Elisabetta Pietrobon" rel="author">Elisabetta Pietrobon</a></span> </span> <span class="meta-tags" title="Tags"> <i class="icon-tags"></i> <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/bruxelles/" rel="tag">Bruxelles</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/fernando-melo/" rel="tag">Fernando Melo</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/florian-leopold-gassmann/" rel="tag">Florian Leopold Gassmann</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/lopera-seria/" rel="tag">L\'Opera seria</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/magnus-staveland/" rel="tag">Magnus Staveland</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/marcos-fink/" rel="tag">Marcos Fink</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/mario-zeffiri/" rel="tag">Mario Zeffiri</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-lirica/" rel="tag">Opera lirica</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/patrick-kinmonth/" rel="tag">Patrick Kinmonth</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/pietro-spagnoli/" rel="tag">Pietro Spagnoli</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/rene-jacobs/" rel="tag">Ren Jacobs</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/robin-johannsen/" rel="tag">Robin Johannsen</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/sunhae-im/" rel="tag">Sunhae Im</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/theatre-la-monnaie/" rel="tag">Thtre La Monnaie</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/thomas-walker/" rel="tag">Thomas Walker</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Bruxelles, Fernando Melo, Florian Leopold Gassmann, L\'Opera seria, Magnus Staveland, Marcos Fink, Mario Zeffiri, Opera lirica, Patrick Kinmonth, Pietro Spagnoli, Ren Jacobs, Robin Johannsen, Sunhae Im, Thtre La Monnaie, Thomas Walker"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/77892c8d7db2bbd3fc7bcb8a46516949" alt="" /> <img src="http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/77892c8d7db2bbd3fc7bcb8a46516949?s=100&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" width="100" height="100" alt="" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 photo avatar-default" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Elisabetta Pietrobon"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/elisabetta-pietrobon/">View all articles by Elisabetta Pietrobon</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2016/02/gioachino-rossini-pesaro-1792-passy-de-paris-1868-il-barbiere-di-siviglia-o-sia-linutil-precauzione/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Gioachino Rossini (1792 1868): &#8220;Il barbiere di Siviglia, o sia L&#8217;inutil precauzione&#8221;</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2016/02/attila-al-teatro-massimo-di-palermo-2/" rel="next">&#8220;Attila&#8221; al Teatro Massimo di Palermo <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"></div></div></div></div><div id="secondary" class="widget-area span4 sb-4" role="complementary"> <aside id="search-4" class="widget widget_search clearfix"><h3 class="widget-title">RICERCA</h3><form method="get" id="searchform" action="http://www.gbopera.it/"> <label for="s" class="assistive-text">Search</label> <input type="text" class="field" name="s" id="